sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CodeFlare SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MCAD as MCAD Controller<br/>Embedded in Manager
    participant InstaScale as InstaScale Controller<br/>Optional
    participant MachineAPI as Machine API Operator
    participant Cloud as Cloud Provider API
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,Cloud: Flow 1: AppWrapper Creation and Scheduling

    User->>K8sAPI: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Watch notification<br/>Internal
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: GET resource availability<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Resource status
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: CREATE wrapped resources<br/>(Pods, Jobs, RayClusters)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: AppWrapper dispatched

    Note over User,Cloud: Flow 2: InstaScale Auto-Scaling (When Enabled)

    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: WATCH pending AppWrappers<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>InstaScale: Pending workload detected
    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: GET current MachineSet replicas<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>InstaScale: MachineSet status
    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: PATCH MachineSet replicas<br/>Scale up<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    MachineAPI->>Cloud: Provision VMs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
    Cloud-->>MachineAPI: New nodes created

    Note over User,Cloud: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>MCAD: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No Auth
    MCAD-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics<br/>Queue depth, dispatch rate
